1
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:04,880
Why is the place such a mess?

2
00:00:05,880 --> 00:00:09,090
Sorry, I was exhausted last night
and just left it.

3
00:00:09,090 --> 00:00:11,340
Don't give me "too tired."

4
00:00:11,340 --> 00:00:13,350
It's only been one day.

5
00:00:13,930 --> 00:00:15,060
I already said I'm sorry.

6
00:00:15,850 --> 00:00:17,560
Instant noodle bowls left out,

7
00:00:17,560 --> 00:00:19,730
half-empty plastic bottles,

8
00:00:19,730 --> 00:00:22,310
and shirts and socks thrown everywhere.
What is wrong with you?

9
00:00:22,310 --> 00:00:24,320
Ugh, give me a break.

10
00:00:24,320 --> 00:00:25,940
I'm exhausted from work.

11
00:00:25,940 --> 00:00:27,570
No matter how tired you are,
can't you at least throw out the trash?

12
00:00:27,570 --> 00:00:29,650
Didn't you just get back
from hanging out yourself?

13
00:00:30,530 --> 00:00:32,120
What's that supposed to mean?

14
00:00:32,120 --> 00:00:35,660
How could a student understand
the struggles of a working adult?

15
00:00:41,790 --> 00:00:44,960
You've changed.

16
00:00:47,260 --> 00:00:51,430
Whatever. I'm taking a shower.
